headline: AIG Taps CVC to Put Its Investment Engine in a Higher Gear
summary: AIG teams up with CVC to deploy nearly $3.5B into private credit and equity secondaries, looking for scalable alternatives.

headline: AIZ Boosts Post-Purchase Capabilities With RL Circular Operations
summary: Assurant acquires RL Circular Operations to reinforce post-purchase and expand its circular logistics footprint in Australia and New Zealand.

headline: Assurant Earnings Preview: What to Expect
summary: Assurant is all set to report its fourth-quarter earnings results next month, and analysts project its EPS to rise impressively.
